Package: frame
Type: Package
Title: Fire Research and Modelling Environment
Version: 0.4.1
Date: 2021-12-23
Authors@R: as.person( c(
    "Philip Zylstra <pzylstra@uow.edu.au> [cre]",
    "Michael Bedward <michael.bedward@gmail.com> [aut]",
    "Soroush Homayounpour <soroush@uow.edu.au> [aut]"))
Description: This package provides an interface to the forest flammability model of Zylstra et al (2016), updated to include the fire effects models of Zylstra (2021). Release four extends this to include functions for processing field survey data into vegetation trends and automatically formatted files for fire behaviour modelling. Version 0.4.1 includes functions for interfacing with 'plant' (Falster et al 2016) to model fire behaviour for a dynamic vegetation model. The package includes a distribution of the model and its dependencies in the form of Java jar files. FRaME requires an installation of Java version 1.8 (aka Java 8) or higher on the host system, with RTools and a minimum of R3.5.
